二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Long/author-zXqLC4s6DtXyk08JOvynSg">Trần Tử Long</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Cao-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-th%C6%B0-k%C3%BD/poem-4_3r_tUgn4sXO_w33S1XKA">Tống Cao tam thập ngũ thư ký - 送高三十五書記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%97i/Tu%E1%BA%BF-m%E1%BB%99-Ph%C3%BAc-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-0ZTYkvhun1R1q8E-tyimOw">Tuế mộ Phúc Xương hoài cổ - 歲暮福昌懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%97i/author-5d8o2S_RIMOZD_yipGScpw">Trương Lỗi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BA%A1c-mi%E1%BA%BFu-to%E1%BA%A1i-t%C3%BAc-nh%E1%BA%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-m%C3%B4n-l%C3%A2u/poem-Fi0Gv61h-zHA0H8Q_95dwg">Yết Hành nhạc miếu toại túc nhạc tự đề môn lâu - 謁衡岳廟遂宿嶽寺題門樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
